com.example.SDLA

Class Note

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.SDLA.Note
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class Note
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    Custom data class to represent a note. A note, assigned to a subject, consists of a title, some textual content, and a timestamp of when it was made.
